---------------------------------------
-- Install the Observations database --
---------------------------------------

Nb : PostGis must be installed.


1) Create a database then get on the server the following PostGis SQL file :
       o lwpostgis.sql
       o spatial_ref_sys.sql

2) Create a schema "postgis".


3) Add the following instruction at the top of each script got previoulsy and execute them :
       Set search_path= Postgis ;


4) Execute then the following scripts:

    o structure Observations.sql

5) Modify and execute the scripts rights.sql.



